    "creatureType": "undead",
    "description": "<p>Shades are the souls of the quiet dead, called back through the Last Door — or perhaps merely echoes of a dead person's personality, given shape by magic. Either way, they might be called up at the Crossroads, via an arcanum, or by some other form of necromancy. A shade can ride a living, willing host (or one properly prepared), withstanding daylight only with great effort, experiencing what its host experiences and communicating only through impulse and desire.</p>",
